OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrook House: Spice drug    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftested on young detainee,  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Finquiry told               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Detainees at an immigration removal    
OL,6, centre tested the drug spice on a      
OL,7, younger man, an undercover BBC reporter
OL,8, has told a public inquiry.             
OL,10,FCallum Tulley told the inquiry into    
OL,11,Fmistreatment of detainees at Brook     
OL,12,FHouse that use of the drug was         
OL,13,Fwidespread.                            
OL,15,FHe said he had been told by two        
OL,16,Fofficers that a batch of spice had been
OL,17,Fsmuggled into the centre.              
OL,19,FIt was given to the young detainee to  
OL,20,Fsee what effect it would have, he said.
